latestIgtvVideos.title: Mother Sparsh new skin care launch.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Winter brings most of our worry when it comes to our skin care. Choosing the right products for your skin is very important especially in this kind of weather where you have dry and flaky skin. 

@mothersparsh recently launched their skin care products and sent me over some.

1) Ultra Rich Face Wash
2) Ultra Rick Face Cream
3) Under Eye Recovery Gel
4) Shea & Cocoa Body Butter
5) Oatmeal & Honey Face Mask

 I am going to use them for a few days before I share my reviews with you. 

Stay Tuned.

Love ❤️ 
Srishty

latestIgtvVideos.title: Rosy Pink Eyes
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello! Hello!

After a long long time, I'm back with another make up video.
Been ages since I made one.

So, this is the most common make up that would go with any look, be it with traditionals or westerns. 
"Rosy pink" is what I call this look. Softly done pink eyes with soft blush cheeks, combined with nude lip shade.

Hope you guys enjoy watching it 💗
Kindly, share your reviews in the comment section.🙏🏻
